## How to Run

1. Clone the repository  
2. Install required dependencies  
3. Open the Jupyter Notebook  
4. Run all cells to reproduce analysis and visualizations  

---

## Limitations

- Dataset does not include user-level behavior (watch time, preferences)  
- Analysis is based on metadata rather than engagement metrics  
- External factors like production delays are inferred, not directly measured  

